data.description: Charming and very well-kept single-family, located on a very nice road, surrounded by many other attractive houses; CBS construction with city water & sewer, & NO HOA fee!  Close to shopping, dining, interstate access & US 1/Federal Highway.  PGT windows & doors, custom-fitted galvanized steel shutters, seamless gutters, and 18'' porcelain tiles in the kitchen & great room. AC and water heater were replaced in 2021 & and the kitchen was renovated with a granite countertop and SS appliances. The master bedroom has a large walk-in closet. Both baths were renovated. Interior laundry room, usable attic space for storage, and a generous east-facing backyard; there is space for a pool! No HOA fee!  Easy to show on Supra! Please find the Supra Box attached to the tree in front of the house.
